     Description
     Measures EarthÂ’s radiation to determine the vertical distribution of
     temperature, moisture and pressure in the atmosphere.  Primary
     instrument for satisfying 3 EDRs

     Heritage or similar sensors
     NASA - Atmospheric Infrared Sounder (AIRS)
     EUMETSAT - Infrared Atmospheric Sounding Interferometer Radiometer
     (IASI)
     POES - High-reslolution infrared sensor (HIRS)
